body.name: SEDETA White Computer Desk with Drawers, 55" Home Office Desk with File Drawer and Storage Shelves, L Shaped Gaming Desk with LED Lights and Monitor Shelf
features: 【Multifunctional Computer Desk】Create a versatile workstation that’ll meet all your needs with this all-in-one white desk with a large computer desktop, monitor riser, file drawer, storage shelves, printer cabinet, and LED lights; An ideal computer desk for small rooms or limited spaces to create excellent home office space.

【Desk with Drawers】Don't know how to store various sizes of documents? Don't worry, the SEDETA computer desk with a file drawer can hold 3 sizes of files - Legal/Letter/A4, and a box drawer can place home or office items. The 5-layer storage shelves can be for full-size printers, files, books, or other items, leaving large space for writing, studying, and other home office desk activities.

【Spacious Working Space】55"(L)*18.89"(W) dimension can easily accommodate your laptop, books, files, and desk accessories. The large workstation can hold 2 computers at the same time. Use this computer monitor riser to easily raise your monitor to just the right height, reduce back and neck strain and pain, and free up tons of workspace below.

【Cool & Smart LED Light Strips 】The white computer desk comes with an RGB LED light strip, remote control via APP, Over 60000 colors, and 29 flashing modes for you to choose from. LED light strip with music sync function, built-in sensitivity adjustable mic, led light color will change with the rhythm of the sound and music. And with the timer function, just enjoy it in a smart way, creating a gaming and a working atmosphere. Light Up Your Gaming with an LED Light Strip.

【Easy Assemble & After-sales Service】To make assembling this sturdy computer desk as effortless as possible, we have included clear and detailed instructions, and numbered parts. If your white desk arrives damaged, scratched, or missing part, please feel free to contact us, we will send you a free replacement or offer a partial refund

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Took a while to assemble, Drawers don't work
reviews.reviewText: I figured out the assembly pretty easily and everything was marked ok but the drawers were not lining up. I still don't have them in a usable manner yet as once you close the drawer it is STUCK. I cannot get them to open again without almost tearing the whole thing apart. Not real happy with that. I like the monitor stand part and the rest of the desk is nice and seems sturdy. The light is ok except when I was applying it half of the sticky part ripped right off so I had to use something else to attach it. Overall I like the look of it but hopefully I can get the drawer problem sorted out.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 10, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Careful attention to the assembly details required
reviews.reviewText: We purchased 2 of these desk to suite our particular needs. The assembly isn't difficult but it is precise. All the parts a labeled. When constructing the desk you need to be aware of the orientation of the rods. The holes in the rods accommodate the bolts and screws. However, if you make a mistake, lie we did a couple times, making the corrections is easy.It is a heavy stable desk with a small drawer that accommodates a desk organizer and a file drawer that will accommodate small or legal hanging file folders. The drawer isn't particularly deep but is is sufficient if you don't have a tremendous number of folders.I like that the monitor sits above the desk top which give me full use of the desk top. The desk top sits at a good hight form myself and my husband. There is adequate shelf space and an open grate shelf if you need to put a CPU somewhere that needs some air circulation.Overall, we are happy with the purchase. I feel that it is appropriately priced considering the quality and the precision that it has.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 19, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful desk, not as easy to assemble as I thought.
reviews.reviewText: The desk looks really nice, and I love all the storage space! It makes work for me a lot easier. The monitor stand seems a little high for me, but I need to check if I can adjust my monitor first. Now, the biggest con for me was the assembly. I’ve assembled many things like this before, so I assumed this would be no different. It took me about 4 hours to assemble and I had to back track several times to make sure that I got it right. The drawers still don’t fit quite right. I’ll have to see what I missed to fix them. The instructions were okay, but for me it was easy to miss some of holes on the instructions meaning that sometimes it was upside down. Overall a good product, but I would have appreciated clearer instructions.Update: I’ve had this desk for about a year now, and it’s not that sturdy. I mentioned before how the drawers didn’t fit right, and as hard as I tried they never did fit and eventually broke due to me trying to fix them. I still like the desk, I replaced the drawers with some sterilite plastic ones but I’m not sure if I’d buy this desk again.
